title: Array Grouping by Multiple Attributes
description: Write a program to group a list of objects by multiple attributes and print the resulting groups.
sample_input: [{name: 'John', age: 25, city: 'New York'}, {name: 'Jane', age: 25, city: 'New York'}, {name: 'Bob', age: 30, city: 'Chicago'}]
sample_output: {25: {New York: [{name: 'John', age: 25, city: 'New York'}, {name: 'Jane', age: 25, city: 'New York'}] and Chicago: []} and 30: {Chicago: [{name: 'Bob', age: 30, city: 'Chicago'}] and New York: []}}
